    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer190211940" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer635237621274976168">Mishima lived his s&amp;m, militaristic, uber-masculine/gay fantasies. In his 20s he bared his feelings in this troubling, often astonishing, novel where desire is an evil spirit to get drunk on. Life, as he <br/>sees it, is a deceptive &quot;show&quot; in false face, headlining naked<br/>players in a series of tableaux depicting Beauty, Sex, Death. And the show, which spotlights lovelessness in Loveland, must always go on.</span>
  <span id="freeText635237621274976168" style="display:none">Mishima lived his s&amp;m, militaristic, uber-masculine/gay fantasies. In his 20s he bared his feelings in this troubling, often astonishing, novel where desire is an evil spirit to get drunk on. Life, as he <br />sees it, is a deceptive "show" in false face, headlining naked<br />players in a series of tableaux depicting Beauty, Sex, Death. And the show, which spotlights lovelessness in Loveland, must always go on.</span>
