        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3169720283" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9311671881163247997">A work in which the internal world of the author explodes into a painful ecosystem of archetypes. Despite their fantastic conception - no one like Mrs. Kaburagi or Yuichi exists in reality - the novel somehow works at both levels, as a dramatic depiction of relationships and events and as a display of these clashing archetypes, which is surely a testament to the author&apos;s genius. </span>
  <span id="freeText9311671881163247997" style="display:none">A work in which the internal world of the author explodes into a painful ecosystem of archetypes. Despite their fantastic conception - no one like Mrs. Kaburagi or Yuichi exists in reality - the novel somehow works at both levels, as a dramatic depiction of relationships and events and as a display of these clashing archetypes, which is surely a testament to the author's genius. </span>
  <a data-text-id="9311671881163247997" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
