      var newTip = new Tip($('bookCover_14028'), "\n\n  <h2><a class=\"readable bookTitle\" href=\"https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/14028.Snow_Country?from_choice=false&amp;from_home_module=false\">Snow Country<\/a><\/h2>\n\n      <div>\n        by <a class=\"authorName\" href=\"/author/show/8550.Yasunari_Kawabata?a=9&amp;origin=related_works\">Yasunari Kawabata<\/a>\n      <\/div>\n\n          <div class=\"smallText uitext darkGreyText\">\n            <span class=\"minirating\"><span class=\"stars staticStars notranslate\"><span size=\"12x12\" class=\"staticStar p10\"><\/span><span size=\"12x12\" class=\"staticStar p10\"><\/span><span size=\"12x12\" class=\"staticStar p10\"><\/span><span size=\"12x12\" class=\"staticStar p6\"><\/span><span size=\"12x12\" class=\"staticStar p0\"><\/span><\/span> 3.66 avg rating &mdash; 22,088 ratings<\/span>            &mdash; published 1948\n          <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"addBookTipDescription\">\n      \n<span id=\"freeTextContainer8526095732557454830\">Nobel Prize recipient Yasunari Kawabata&apos;s Snow Country is widely considered to be the writer&apos;s masterpiece, a powerful tale of wasted love set amid the desolate beauty of western Japan.\n\nAt an isolated mountain hot spring, with snow blanketing every <\/span>\n  <span id=\"freeText8526095732557454830\" style=\"display:none\">Nobel Prize recipient Yasunari Kawabata\'s Snow Country is widely considered to be the writer\'s masterpiece, a powerful tale of wasted love set amid the desolate beauty of western Japan.\n\nAt an isolated mountain hot spring, with snow blanketing every surface, Shimamura, a wealthy dilettante meets Komako, a lowly geisha. She gives herself to him fully and without remorse, despite knowing that their passion cannot last and that the affair can have only one outcome. In chronicling the course of this doomed romance, Kawabata has created a story for the ages, a stunning novel dense in implication and exalting in its sadness.<\/span>\n  <a dat